descriptionHtml: Halem's House is a new player home. Players must complete a short quest to unlock the house. This home is located just outside of Riverwood and features a workshop, a 24 hour vendor, shrines, and a training room. The training room in the basement is a simple set up - pull the chain, spawn a bandit to fight. Also in this mod is a small mine outside the house.
